items.title: The Impossible Rules of 'Gentle Parenting'
items.description: Parents are pushing back on their authoritarian upbringings. Now they talk about big feelings and gentle hands.

items.title: If You're Checking That Bag, It Better Have an AirTag
items.description: Make sure the battery isn’t low and turn on Lost Mode—even if the luggage isn’t lost—for more frequent alerts.

items.title: Apple's App Store Puts Kids a Click Away From a Slew of Inappropriate Apps
items.description: An analysis recommends that Apple, an emerging target for digital-safety advocates, apply an independent review for software age ratings.

items.title: How Scammers Are Using AI This Holiday Season to Steal Your Money
items.description: Fake licenses and passports are being generated to fraudulently verify identities—among other techniques.

items.title: The Next Great Leap in AI Is Behind Schedule and Crazy Expensive
items.description: OpenAI has run into problem after problem on its new artificial-intelligence project, code-named Orion.
